      "title": "EduaakashaA — NIRF 2026 Engineering Rankings",
      "bodyText": "EduaakashaA\n\nNIRF ENGINEERING RANKINGS · ANALYTICS DASHBOARD\n\nNIRF 2026\nMoE India · nirfindia.org\n300 Institutions · 4 Bands\n📊 Overview\n🏆 All Rankings\n⭐ Top 10\n📍 State vs Rank\n📈 Analytics\n🔄 Compare\n🔍 State Drill-Down\n300\nTOTAL INSTITUTIONS\n4 rank bands\n100\nRANKED 1–100\nWith NIRF scores\n88.72\nTOP SCORE\nIIT Madras #1\n32\nSTATES COVERED\nPan-India\n58\nTAMIL NADU\nMost colleges\n#20\nANNA UNIVERSITY\nScore: 63.51\n🏉 Top 5 Engineering Colleges — NIRF 2026\n#1\nIndian Institute of Technology Madras\nChennai, Tamil Nadu · IIT\n88.72/100\n🌐 Visit Website\n#2\nIndian Institute of Technology Delhi\nNew Delhi, Delhi · IIT\n85.74/100\n🌐 Visit Website\n#3\nIndian Institute of Technology Bombay\nMumbai, Maharashtra · IIT\n83.65/100\n🌐 Visit Website\n#4\nIndian Institute of Technology Kanpur\nKanpur, Uttar Pradesh · IIT\n81.82/100\n🌐 Visit Website\n#5\nIndian Institute of Technology Kharagpur\nKharagpur, West Bengal · IIT\n78.69/100\n🌐 Visit Website\nSTATE DISTRIBUTION (TOP 12)\nINSTITUTION TYPES\nSCORE DISTRIBUTION (RANK 1–100)\n📋 Rank Band Summary\n🏉 Rank 1–100\nInstitutions\n100\nScores\nAvailable\nTop Score\n88.72 (IIT Madras)\n🥈 Rank 101–150\nInstitutions\n50\nScores\nNot available\nOrdering\nAlphabetical\n🥉 Rank 151–200\nInstitutions\n51\nScores\nNot available\nOrdering\nAlphabetical\n📋 Rank 201–300\nInstitutions\n99\nScores\nNot available\nOrdering\nAlphabetical\n⚠️\n\nEduaakashaA Analytics — NIRF Engineering Rankings 2026\n300 institutions, 4 bands. Ranks 1–100 carry official NIRF scores; bands 101–300 listed alphabetically per NIRF policy. Source: NIRF · nirfindia.org | MoE, Government of India. Subject to error. Verify at nirfindia.org.",
